[["59b61e0c-238e-4351-8136-9eef1a31e005","b2c0f525-db91-48e2-96c5-5359e5eea878","18b9b9e6-f51a-40a4-93fd-49992dd03a91","b7e578b8-9211-48f8-96a5-7642b4b86c97","326e291f-3d48-4ae1-ab6c-88eed7918aea","68384ef4-2b3a-4bb4-8aba-76e261c8c70f","d7431259-d33e-46e8-96ff-f45f449bbc38","c468509e-d670-408b-a935-67183f02079e","ca463886-94f6-4888-a601-f6ea5ca6694f","de4595d6-177a-46d3-87f5-b394e56639a8","b664640e-b6fe-4e33-b08b-15c978f4c1d6","71aea5fa-9fe4-4951-b682-836e0eaf5b01","3820d6fa-956a-47a8-befe-9f427f69b06c","8db40607-4958-45ca-8ed9-81ef24e6fbba"],{"id":"b2c0f525-db91-48e2-96c5-5359e5eea878","title":"1.%20The%20Gig","author":"Alex%20Loret%20de%20Mola","created":"2026-05-17T18:17:58.344Z","updated":"2026-06-25T14:08:44.545Z","narrative":"It%20has%20been%206%20months%20since%20the%20formation%20of%20Huntr%2Fx%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20have%20been%20playing%20at%20small%20venues%2C%20trying%20to%20gain%20exposure%20and%20practice.%20%20Tonight%2C%20they're%20playing%20for%20a%20small%20crowd%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20a%20busy%20riverside%20district.%20%20Or%20at%20least%2C%20that%20was%20the%20plan.%20%20As%20they%20were%20getting%20ready%20in%20the%20green%20room%2C%20they%20were%20ambushed%20by%20uninvited%20demon%20guests!%0A%0AGo%20room%20to%20room%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20demons%20are%20taken%20care%20of%20before%20they%20cause%20problems.%0A%0AEach%20hero%20will%20receive%20500gp%20as%20a%20reward%20for%20removing%20the%20demons!%0A%0AHeroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20Chapter%201%3A%20The%20Gig.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20-%20This%20marks%20the%20starting%20area%20for%20the%20heroes.%0A%0A**A**%20-%20*%22A%20goblin%20appeared%20while%20you%20were%20getting%20ready%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20venue%20tonight!%20%20Ready%20your%20weapons%2C%20girls!%22*%0A%0AWhen%20they%20search%20this%20room%2C%20instead%20of%20drawing%20a%20treasure%20card%20read%20the%20following%3A%20*%22You%20find%20100gp%20on%20the%20desk%20per%20hero.%20%20That%20was%20going%20to%20be%20your%20pay%20for%20your%20performance%20tonight.%20%20I%20suppose%20it%20can%20be%20pay%20for%20extermination%20services%20instead.%22*%0A%0A**B**%20-%20When%20searching%20this%20room%2C%20instead%20of%20drawing%20a%20treasure%20card%2C%20say%20*%22Amidst%20the%20books%20on%20music%20theory%20and%20history%2C%20you%20find%20a%20Potion%20of%20Healing.%20%20Take%20one%20from%20the%20treasure%20deck.%22*%0A%0A**C**%20-%20When%20searching%20this%20room%2C%20instead%20of%20drawing%20a%20treasure%20card%2C%20say%20*%22This%20looks%20like%20it%20must%20be%20where%20the%20venue%20keeps%20the%20evening's%20earnings.%20%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20go%20through%20their%20valuables%3F%22*%0A%0AIf%20the%20hero%20says%20yes%2C%20do%20a%20standard%20trap%20check.%20%20The%20chest%20has%20an%20electric%20shock%20trap%2C%20and%20if%20not%20disarmed%20it%20deals%20one%20BP%20damage%20to%20the%20hero.%20%20The%20heroes%20find%20100gp%20per%20hero%20inside.%0A%0A**D**%20-%20This%20door%20begins%20open%2C%20with%20the%20enemies%20in%20the%20next%20room%20ready%20to%20fight%20alongside%20the%20Fimir.%0A%0A**E**%20-%20*%22As%20you%20enter%20the%20room%2C%20you%20see%20one%20of%20the%20demons%20enveloping%20a%20human%20in%20purple%20mist.%20%20He%20utters%20in%20a%20sinister%20tone%3A%20'In%20the%20name%20of%20my%20master%2C%20Agwi%20Hwasin%2C%20and%20of%20the%20malice%20hidden%20in%20your%20soul%2C%20stand%20and%20become%20one%20of%20us.'%20%20To%20your%20horror%2C%20the%20person%20disappears%20in%20the%20purple%20mist%20and%20is%20replaced%20by%20a%20terrifying%20zombie.%22*%0A%0AWhen%20these%20demons%20are%20defeated%2C%20say%20*%22You're%20pretty%20sure%20that%20was%20the%20last%20of%20them.%20%20What%20just%20happened%3F%20%20You've%20seen%20demons%20consume%20human%20souls%2C%20but%20you've%20never%20seen%20them%20turn%20one%20into%20a%20demon.%20%20And%20who%20is%20this%20master%2C%20Agwi%20Hwasin%2C%20of%20which%20they%20spoke%3F%20%20You%20need%20to%20get%20out%20of%20here%20and%20find%20answers.%20%20Celine%20might%20know%20about%20this%20demon%20and%20what%20to%20do%20next.%22*","wanderingMonster":"Goblin","style":"hq-us","layout":"defaultMap","map":{"H3":{"furniture":"alchemistsbenchS"},"G5":{"creature":"goblin","door":"doorE"},"F9":{"door":"doorE"},"C10":{"door":"doorW"},"C6":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterD"},"E1":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"A15":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"G15":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"G12":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"G13":{"door":"doorS"},"G14":{"door":"doorS"},"J11":{"furniture":"cupboardE"},"J16":{"furniture":"fireplaceE"},"E9":{"creature":"goblin"},"G9":{"creature":"goblin"},"F8":{"creature":"orc"},"C11":{"creature":"skeleton"},"D10":{"creature":"goblin"},"D12":{"creature":"goblin"},"D11":{"creature":"orc"},"C8":{"creature":"abomination"},"C2":{"door":"doorW"},"C4":{"creature":"orc"},"B4":{"creature":"goblin"},"D4":{"creature":"goblin"},"A4":{"creature":"skeleton"},"A12":{"creature":"skeleton"},"E13":{"creature":"goblin"},"E14":{"creature":"goblin"},"K13":{"creature":"abomination"},"K14":{"creature":"abomination"},"B11":{"furniture":"chestN"},"B12":{"furniture":"throneN"},"I8":{"furniture":"bookcaseN"},"H4":{"annotation":"letterA"},"H8":{"annotation":"letterB"},"C12":{"annotation":"letterC"},"J13":{"annotation":"letterE"},"F1":{"annotation":"rock"},"G1":{"annotation":"rock"},"I1":{"annotation":"rock"},"J1":{"annotation":"rock"},"K1":{"annotation":"rock"},"L1":{"annotation":"rock"},"M1":{"annotation":"rock"},"H1":{"annotation":"rock"},"N1":{"annotation":"rock"},"O1":{"annotation":"rock"},"P1":{"annotation":"rock"},"Q1":{"annotation":"rock"},"R1":{"annotation":"rock"},"S1":{"annotation":"rock"},"S2":{"annotation":"rock"},"S3":{"annotation":"rock"},"S4":{"annotation":"rock"},"S5":{"annotation":"rock"},"S6":{"annotation":"rock"},"S7":{"annotation":"rock"},"S8":{"annotation":"rock"},"S9":{"annotation":"rock"},"S10":{"annotation":"rock"},"S11":{"annotation":"rock"},"S12":{"annotation":"rock"},"S13":{"annotation":"rock"},"S1