%20reveal%20more%20about%20this%20demon%20and%20how%20it%20can%20be%20confronted.%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20Chapter%203%3A%20The%20Ambush.%0A%0ACeline%20tells%20you%20to%20rest%2C%20and%20that%20she%20will%20make%20preparations%20for%20her%20trip%20in%20the%20morning.%20%20However%2C%20as%20night%20falls%20on%20Jeju%20island%20you%20find%20yourself%20suddenly%20confronted%20by%20a%20small%20army%20of%20demons%20who%20appear%20out%20of%20nowhere!%20%20How%20did%20they%20manage%20to%20ambush%20even%20this%20sacred%20place%3F%0A%0AAmidst%20the%20chaos%2C%20Celine%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found.%20%20You%20have%20to%20find%20her!","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20%3D%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%0A%0A**A**%20%3D%20When%20they%20first%20open%20either%20of%20these%20doors%2C%20reveal%20the%20two%20characters%20at%20(A)%20and%20say%20the%20following%3A%0A%0A*As%20you%20rush%20out%20the%20door%2C%20you%20see%20a%20horrible%20monstrosity%20in%20the%20distance%3A%20could%20this%20be%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20himself%3F%20%20He%20is%20dragging%20an%20unconscious%20Celine%20with%20him!%20%20He%20speaks%20unintelligible%20words%20at%20a%20nearby%20wall%2C%20shattering%20it%20into%20a%20million%20pieces%20and%20he%20drags%20Celine%20away%20into%20the%20cloud%20of%20smoke.*%0A%0AWith%20this%2C%20reveal%20the%20secret%20door%20next%20to%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20at%20(A)%20and%20remove%20him%20and%20Celine%20from%20the%20board.%0A%0A**B**%20%3D%20Upon%20opening%20any%20of%20these%20doors%2C%20all%20three%20of%20them%20immediately%20open%20and%20the%20contents%20become%20visible%2Factive.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*You%20can%20see%20the%20heavy%2C%20dirty%20footprints%20of%20a%20demon%20that%20came%20through%20here%20recently%3A%20but%20you%20are%20not%20alone%20here!*%0A%0A**C**%20%3D%20Upon%20opening%20any%20of%20these%20doors%2C%20all%20three%20of%20them%20immediately%20open%20and%20the%20contents%20become%20visible%2Factive.%20%20Turn%20the%20furniture%20in%20these%20rooms%20on%20their%20sides%20or%20back%20to%20make%20it%20look%20ransacked.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*This%20must%20have%20been%20Celine's%20apartment.%20%20The%20place%20looks%20ransacked.%20%20These%20demons%20are%20looking%20for%20something.*%0A%0AWhen%20searched%2C%20say%20*Celine%20kept%20a%20Potion%20of%20Healing%20in%20her%20desk%20drawer%2C%20as%20well%20as%20100gp%20per%20hero.%20%20It%20seems%20to%20still%20be%20intact.%20%20You%20take%20it.*%20(Provide%20the%20potion%20of%20healing%20as%20a%20reward%20instead%20of%20pulling%20from%20the%20Treasure%20deck)%0A%0A**D**%20%3D%20Upon%20opening%20any%20of%20these%20doors%2C%20all%20three%20of%20them%20immediately%20open%20and%20the%20contents%20become%20visible%2Factive.%20%20Turn%20this%20furniture%20askew%20as%20well%20to%20indicate%20it%20is%20also%20ransacked.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*How%20did%20they%20do%20so%20much%20damage%20so%20quickly%3F%20%20They%20must%20be%20desperate.%20%20You%20have%20to%20keep%20going%20and%20find%20Celine!*%0A%0A**E**%20%3D%20When%20opening%20these%20doors%2C%20place%20the%20contents%20of%20this%20room%20and%20say%3A%0A%0A*There%20they%20are!%20%20You%20spot%20the%20demon%20and%20the%20still-unconscious%20Celine.%20%20It%20turns%20to%20you%20and%20stares%20into%20your%20soul%20with%20eyes%20of%20ancient%20flame%2C%20and%20then%20scoffs.%20%20%22There%20is%20nothing%20you%20can%20do%20to%20stop%20what%20I%20will%20unleash%20on%20the%20world.%20%20If%20you%20want%20your%20mentor%20back%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20take%20her%20from%20me...%20if%20you%20can.%22%0A%0AWith%20a%20deafening%20roar%20and%20a%20momentary%20glimpse%20of%20the%20unbearable%20heat%20of%20the%20underworld%20at%20their%20feet%2C%20Celine%20and%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20disappear%20into%20the%20earth.%20%20The%20hole%20that%20opened%20below%20them%20closes%20as%20suddenly%20as%20it%20opened%2C%20leaving%20no%20trace%20of%20how%20to%20follow%20them%20into%20the%20underworld.*%0A%0ATake%20Celine%20and%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20off%20of%20the%20board.%0A%0A*The%20demon%20left%20behind%20an%20intimidating%20looking%20minion%3A%20the%20mummy%20that%20stands%20before%20you%20looks%20particularly%20fearsome%2C%20and%20his%20bandages%20crackle%20with%20purple%20energy.%20%20Prepare%20to%20defend%20yourselves!*%0A%0A**F**%20%3D%20This%20empowered%20Mummy%20has%20the%20following%20statistics%3A%0A%0AAttack%20dice%3A%204%0ADefense%20dice%3A%204%0AMovement%3A%204%0ABody%20Points%3A%206%0AMind%20Points%3A%200%20(Undead)%0AType%3A%20Mindless%0AManeuver%3A%20Intimidate%0ASpecial%3A%20Heroes%20who%20end%20their%20turn%20in%20line%20of%20sight%20of%20the%20monster%20take%201%20Body%20Point%20of%20damage%20unless%20they%20succeed%20on%20a%20Mind%20Check%2C%20from%20the%20corrupting%20power%20of%20the%20purple%20energy%20emanating%20from%20his%20body.%0A%0AOnce%20defeated%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*The%20girls%20survey%20the%20damage%20done%20by%20the%20demons.%20%20Among%20the%20wreckage%2C%20they%20find%20600gp%20each%20that%20Celine%20must%20have%20been%20saving%20for%20an%20emergency.%20%20I%20think%20she'd%20understand%20if%20now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20use%20it.%0A%0ARumi%20narrows%20her%20eyes.%20%20%22If%20we're%20going%20to%20save%20Celine%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20follow%20her%2C%20and%20what%20we're%20facing.%20%20It%20looks%20like%20we%20have%20a%20date%20at%20the%20Library.%22*%0A","wanderingMonster":"Orc","style":"hq-us"},{"id":"326e291f-3d48-4ae1-ab6c-88eed7918aea","title":"4.%20The%20Library%20of%20Jang","author":"","created":"2026-06-15T12:33:46.385Z","updated":"2026-06-25T13:44:27.743Z","layout":"defaultMap","map":{"J14":{"annotation":"letterA"},"C3":{"door":"staircaseN"},"B4":{"annotation":"letterX"},"Q24":{"annotation":"letterB"},"E10":{"door":"doorW"},"G6":{"door":"doorW"},"D12":{"door":"doorE","annotation":"letterL"},"D15":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterD"},"D18":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterD"},"D22":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterD"},"C5":{"door":"doorE"},"C9":{"do