"annotation":"rock"},"K3":{"annotation":"rock"},"K4":{"annotation":"rock"},"K5":{"annotation":"rock"},"K6":{"annotation":"rock"},"K7":{"annotation":"rock"},"K8":{"annotation":"rock"},"K9":{"annotation":"rock"},"L9":{"annotation":"rock"},"M9":{"annotation":"rock"},"N9":{"annotation":"rock"},"O9":{"annotation":"rock"},"O8":{"annotation":"rock"},"O7":{"annotation":"rock"},"O6":{"annotation":"rock"},"O5":{"annotation":"rock"},"O4":{"annotation":"rock"},"O3":{"annotation":"rock"},"N3":{"annotation":"rock"},"N4":{"annotation":"rock"},"N5":{"annotation":"rock"},"N6":{"annotation":"rock"},"N7":{"annotation":"rock"},"N8":{"annotation":"rock"},"M8":{"annotation":"rock"},"M7":{"annotation":"rock"},"M6":{"annotation":"rock"},"M5":{"annotation":"rock"},"M4":{"annotation":"rock"},"M3":{"annotation":"rock"},"L3":{"annotation":"rock"},"L4":{"annotation":"rock"},"L5":{"annotation":"rock"},"L6":{"annotation":"rock"},"L7":{"annotation":"rock"},"L8":{"annotation":"rock"},"N10":{"annotation":"rock"},"N11":{"annotation":"rock"},"N12":{"annotation":"rock"},"O12":{"annotation":"rock"},"O11":{"annotation":"rock"},"O10":{"annotation":"rock"},"I1":{"annotation":"rock"},"H1":{"annotation":"rock"},"G1":{"annotation":"rock"},"F1":{"annotation":"rock"},"E1":{"annotation":"rock"},"D1":{"annotation":"rock"},"C1":{"annotation":"rock"},"B1":{"annotation":"rock"},"A1":{"annotation":"rock"},"A2":{"annotation":"rock"},"A3":{"annotation":"rock"},"A4":{"annotation":"rock"},"A5":{"annotation":"rock"},"A6":{"annotation":"rock"},"A7":{"annotation":"rock"},"A8":{"annotation":"rock"},"A9":{"annotation":"rock"},"A10":{"annotation":"rock"},"A11":{"annotation":"rock"},"A12":{"annotation":"rock"},"G3":{"furniture":"alchemistsbenchW"},"E5":{"furniture":"throneN"},"H8":{"furniture":"sorcererstableS"},"B7":{"furniture":"bookcaseN"},"R24":{"furniture":"bookcaseN"},"C24":{"furniture":"tableN"},"B20":{"furniture":"fireplaceN"},"I21":{"annotation":"rock"},"I20":{"annotation":"rock"},"I19":{"annotation":"rock"},"I18":{"annotation":"rock"},"H18":{"annotation":"rock"},"H19":{"annotation":"rock"},"H20":{"annotation":"rock"},"H21":{"annotation":"rock"},"G21":{"annotation":"rock"},"G20":{"annotation":"rock"},"G19":{"annotation":"rock"},"G18":{"annotation":"rock"},"F18":{"annotation":"rock"},"F19":{"annotation":"rock"},"F20":{"annotation":"rock"},"F21":{"annotation":"rock"},"J13":{"furniture":"sorcererstableW"},"M14":{"door":"doorN"},"K20":{"door":"doorN","annotation":"letterI"},"M22":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterI"},"L25":{"furniture":"tombW"},"E7":{"furniture":"cupboardN"},"L18":{"furniture":"bookcaseE"},"G22":{"furniture":"bookcaseE"},"B16":{"furniture":"bookcaseN"},"E9":{"annotation":"letterH"},"P15":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterC"},"P19":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterC"},"P22":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterC"},"P14":{"annotation":"letterJ"},"J18":{"annotation":"letterJ"},"J9":{"annotation":"letterJ"},"B22":{"annotation":"letterJ"},"Q25":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"Q23":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"O24":{"creature":"goblin"},"O25":{"creature":"goblin"},"H24":{"creature":"mummy"},"G5":{"annotation":"letterH"},"L23":{"creature":"zombie"},"M23":{"creature":"zombie"},"N23":{"creature":"mummy"},"K23":{"creature":"abomination"},"F4":{"creature":"abomination"},"H4":{"creature":"abomination"},"G4":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"F7":{"creature":"goblin"},"J3":{"annotation":"letterK"},"D23":{"creature":"skeleton"},"E23":{"creature":"skeleton"},"C19":{"creature":"skeleton"},"E19":{"creature":"skeleton"},"D20":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"C11":{"creature":"orc"},"E11":{"creature":"orc"},"D11":{"creature":"orc"}},"narrative":"Last%20time%2C%20on%20Huntr%2Fx%20Quest...%20%0A%0AAfter%20a%20surprise%20ambush%20at%20Jeju%20Island%2C%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20kidnapped%20Celine%20and%20brought%20her%20into%20the%20underworld.%20%20You%20have%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20pursue%20him%20and%20rescue%20her.%20%20Celine%20had%20mentioned%20the%20Chronicles%20of%20Mudang%3A%20perhaps%20they%20will%20reveal%20some%20information%20that%20would%20help%20you%20in%20your%20quest.%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20Chapter%204%3A%20The%20Library.%0A%0AIt%20was%20a%20treacherous%20three%20day%20journey%20through%20the%20mountain%20trail%20to%20the%20Library%20of%20Jang%2C%20but%20you%20finally%20made%20it.%20%20As%20you%20ascend%20the%20staircase%20from%20the%20ground%20floor%20into%20the%20library%2C%20you%20find%20that%20every%20wall%20seems%20covered%20from%20floor%20to%20ceiling%20with%20books%2C%20as%20if%20the%20walls%20were%20made%20not%20of%20stone%20but%20of%20the%20archives%20themselves.%0A%0AYou%20know%20not%20where%20the%20Chronicles%20of%20Mudang%20are%20held%20within%20this%20sprawling%20library%2C%20but%20you%20remember%20Celine%20mentioning%20that%20a%20central%20room%20held%20a%20paper%20catalog%20where%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20find%20the%20location%20of%20the%20tome.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20-%20The%20Girls%20start%20here.%0A%0A(NOTE%3A%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20bookcases%2C%20they%20are%20purely%20decorative.%20%20Leave%20some%20out.)%0A%0A**A**%20%3D%20When%20they%20enter%20this%20room%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You've%20finally%20found%20it%3A%20the%20catalog%20archives%20of%20the%20Library%20of%20Jang.%20%20Any%20of%20you%20can%20spend%20your%20turn%20searching%20the%20catalog%20for%20the%20location%20of%20the%20Chronicles%2C%20but%20beware%20of%20attack.*%0A%0AAny%20hero%20who%20elects%20to%20search%20the%20catalog%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20take%20any%20action%20other%20than%20performing%20an%20unassisted%20Mind%20Check.%20%20If%20they%20succeed%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20have%20located%20the%20Chronicles%20of%20Mudang!%20%20Head%20over%20there%20to%20retrieve%20it!*%0A%0APoint%20at%20location%20(B)%20on%20the%20map.%20%20Event%20(B)%20can%20now%20be%20activated.%0A%0AWhile%20in%20this%20room%2C%20both%20immediately%20and%20during%20each%20of%20Gwi-Ma's%20turn%20a%20wandering%20monster%20(Orc)%20should%20spawn%20at%20each%20of%20the%20entrances%20to%20this%20room%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%204%20of%20these%20wandering%20monsters%20to%20be%20alive%20at%20any%20time.%20%20Newly%20spawned%20monsters%20do%20not%20take%20their%20turn%20until%20the%20next%20round.%0A%0A**B**%20%3D%20This%20does%20not%20activate%20until%20the%20girls%20have%20completed%20the%20challenge%20in%20(A).%20%20If%20they%20have%2C%20then%20spawn%20creatures%20etc...%20the%20next%20time%20the%20heroes%20can%20see%20through%20or%20open%20the%20door.%0A%0AWhen%20they%20enter%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*The%20demons%20in%20this%20room%20appear%20to%20be%20looking%20for%20something.*%0A%0AOn%20search%2C%20say%20the%20following%20instead%20of%20pulling%20a%20treasure%20card%3A%0A%0A*Reaching%20up%20to%20the%20top%20bookshelf%2C%20you%20pull%20an%20ancient%20grey%20leather%20tome%20down.%20%20In%20gold%20lettering%2C%20the%20front%20reads%20'The%20Chronicles%20of%20Mudang.'%20%20You%20tuck%20it%20under%20your%20arm.%20%20It's%20time%20to%20get%20out%20of%20here.*%0A%0AFrom%20now%20on%3A%20(J)%20is%20active%2C%20replace%20the%20door%20at%20(L)%20with%20a%20Stone%20Tile%2C%20%0A%0A**C**%20%3D%20No%20creatures%20spawn%20here%20even%20if%20they%20open%20the%20door%20unless%20the%20heroes%20have%20completed%20(A).%20%20If%20they%20have%2C%20then%20spawn%20creatures%20etc...%20the%20next%20time%20the%20heroes%20can%20see%20through%20or%20open%20the%20door.%20%20Once%20(A)%20is%20completed%2C%20all%20C%20doors%20open%20when%20any%20one%20opens.%0A%0A**D**%20%3D%20No%20creatures%20spawn%20here%20even%20if%20they%20open%20the%20door%20unless%20the%20heroes%20have%20completed%20(B).%20%20If%20they%20have%2C%20then%20spawn%20creatures%20etc...%20the%20next%20time%20the%20heroes%20can%20see%20through%20or%20open%20the%20door.%20%20Once%20(B)%20is%20completed%2C%20all%20D%20doors%20open%20when%20any%20one%20opens.%0A%0A*The%20wall%20has%20collapsed%3A%20there's%20no%20way%20through!%20%20There%20must%20be%20another%20way%20to%20escape!*%0A%0A**E**%20%3D%20If%20the%20heroes%20have%20completed%20(B)%20and%20clear%20this%20room%2C%20tell%20them%20when%20they%20search%20*You%20notice%20that%20one%20of%20the%20windows%20leading%20out%20to%20the%20ledge%20of%20the%20building%20is%20unlocked.%20%20You%20push%20it%20open.*%20%20And%20then%20reveal%20this%20secret%20door.%0A%0A**F**%20%3D%20When%20the%20girls%20turn%20this%20corner%2C%20tell%20them%3A%0A%0A*You%20see%20what%20might%20be%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20descend%20at%20the%20far%20end%20of%20the%20ledge%3A%20a%20wooden%20scaffolding%20coming%20up%20from%20the%20ground%20that%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20jump%20onto%20and%20climb%20down!%20%20However%2C%20a%20particularly%20tough-looking%20gargoyle%20is%20standing%20between%20you%20and%20it!*%0A%0APlace%20the%20table%20on%20its%20side%20just%20off%20of%20the%20board%2C%20north%20of%20where%20it%20is%20on%20the%20map.%0A%0AThe%20gargoyle%20has%206%20Body%20Points%20instead%20of%20the%20normal%203.%0A%0A**G**%20%3D%20Whenever%20a%20girl%20reaches%20this%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*The%20scaffolding%20looks%20fairly%20rickety%20and%20is%20a%20few%20feet%20below%20you.%20%20You're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20jump%20for%20it.%20%20Make%20a%20body%20check!*%0A%0AHave%20them%20make%20a%20Body%20Check%20(assisted%20if%20there's%20an%20adjacent%20ally%20or%20one%20who%20is%20already%20on%20the%20scaffolding).%20%20If%20they%20fail%2C%20they%20can%20choose%20between%20making%20a%20bad%20jump%20and%20injuring%20themselves%20on%20the%20way%20down%20to%20take%203BP%20of%20damage%2C%20or%20waiting%20for%20their%20next%20turn%20to%20make%20another%20attempt.%0A%0AFor%20every%20Gwi-Ma%20turn%20after%20the%20first%20hero%20reaches%20this%2C%20spawn%20a%20new%20Orc%20wandering%20monster%20at%20F%2C%20with%20no%20limit.%20%20It%20cannot%20move%20or%20attack%20the%20turn%20it%20spawns.%20(this%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20wandering%20monsters%20spawning%20at%20the%20nearest%20J)%0A%0AOnce%20all%20the%20girls%20are%20safely%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*As%20you%20climb%20down%20from%20the%20scaffolding%2C%20you%20can%20hear%20the%20wailing%20of%20demons%20nearby.%20%20Gripping%20the%20old%20leather-bound%20book%20tightly%2C%20you%20make%20a%20hasty%20exit.%20%20You%20girls%20have%20some%20reading%20to%20do.%20%20You%20each%20earn%20300gp%20worth%20of%20experience%20from%20what%20you%20glean%20in%20the%20tome.*%0A%0A**H**%20%3D%20All%20(H)%20doors%20open%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20%20Say%3A%0A%0A*You%20see%20several%20desks%20and%20a%20shelf%20filled%20with%20research%20papers.%20%20You%20wonder%20if%20this%20is%20where%20the%20librarians%20worked.%20%20You%20wonder%20where%20the%20librarians%20are%20now.*%0A%0AWhen%20searched%2C%20instead%20of%20pulling%20from%20the%20treasure%20deck%3A%0A%0A*The%20corpses%20of%20the%20two%20Fimirs%20held%20tattered%20employee%20ID%20cards%3A%20they%20were%20the%20librarians%2C%20before%20being%20corrupted%20by%20the%20power%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin.%20%20You%20are%20glad%20that%20they%20are%20now%20at%20rest.%20%20Rifling%20through%20the%20desk%2C%20you%20find%20important%20historical%20research%20worth%20about%20200gp%20per%20hero.*%0A%0A**I**%20%3D%20All%20(I)%20doors%20open%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20%20Say%3A%0A%0A*Other%20than%20the%20demon%20footprints%20in%20the%20thick%20layer%20of%20dust%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20these%20rooms%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20that%20no%20one%20has%20stepped%20into%20this%20area%20for%20many%20years%3A%20possibly%20even%20decades.%20%20The%20air%20smells%20stale.*%0A%0AWhen%20searched%2C%20instead%20of%20pulling%20from%20the%20treasure%20deck%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*To%20your%20surprise%2C%20you%20find%20a%20long-forgotten%20tomb%20in%20this%20room.%20%20What%20is%20it%20doing%20in%20a%20library%3F%20%20Make%20an%20assisted%20Mind%20Check.*%0A%0AIf%20they%20pass%20the%20mind%20check%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20think%20to%20check%20the%20tomb%20for%20inscriptions.%20%20It%20says%20'Jang%20the%20Librarian%2C%201478-1556.%20%20May%20the%20light%20of%20knowledge%20brighten%20the%20path%20of%20all%20those%20who%20seek%20it%20here.'%20%20You%20feel%20a%20presence%20pass%20through%20you%2C%20and%20suddenly%20your%20mind%20feels%20clearer.%20%20Each%20hero%20gains%20one%20permanent%20upgrade%20to%20her%20Mind%20points%2C%20if%20they%20have%20an%20available%20upgrade%20slot.%20%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20gain%2075gp%20of%20experience.*%0A%0AIf%20they%20fail%20the%20mind%20check%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20decide%20to%20open%20the%20lid%20of%20the%20tomb.%20%20The%20room%20quakes%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20and%20suddenly%20spikes%20shoot%20out%20from%20the%20open%20lid!%20%20Make%20an%20assisted%20Body%20Check%2C%20or%20be%20wounded%20for%202%20Body%20Points.%20%20You%20find%2050gp%20per%20hero%20worth%20of%20old%20documents%20amidst%20some%20long-decaying%20bones.*%0A%0A**J**%20%3D%20Only%20active%20once%20(B)%20is%20completed.%20%20The%20nearest%20(J)%20to%20a%20hero%20will%20spawn%20a%20wandering%20Orc%20here%20during%20each%20of%20Gwi-Ma's%20turns.%20%20It%20does%20not%20move%20or%20attack%20the%20turn%20it%20spawns.%0A%0A**K**%20%3D%20When%20a%20hero%20opens%20this%20chest%2C%20they%20find%20treasure%20worth%20100gp%20per%20hero.%0A%0A**L**%20%3D%20If%20the%20heroes%20have%20completed%20(B)%20and%20come%20to%20this%20door%2C%20replace%20it%20with%20a%20stone%20tile.%20%20","wanderingMonster":"Orc","style":"hq-us"},{"id":"68384ef4-2b3a-4bb4-8aba-76e261c8c70f","title":"5.%20The%20Secrets%20of%20Seoraksan","author":"","created":"2026-06-15T21:27:42.044Z","updated":"2026-06-25T13:45:32.773Z","layout":"defaultMap","map":{"P2":{"annotation":"letterX"},"P6":{"door":"doorW"},"P10":{"door":"doorW"},"N5":{"door":"doorE"},"P4":{"creature":"barbarian"},"P8":{"creature":"dwarf"},"P11":{"creature":"elf"},"L3":{"creature":"wizard"},"L4":{"furniture":"alchemistsbenchE"},"Q8":{"furniture":"weaponsrackN"},"P12":{"furniture":"bookcaseE"},"R4":{"furniture":"fireplaceS"},"R2":{"door":"do