":{"furniture":"rackN"},"R18":{"door":"doorE"},"P20":{"furniture":"sorcererstableN"},"N11":{"creature":"zombie"},"Q20":{"annotation":"letterH"},"R15":{"creature":"abomination"},"Q16":{"creature":"gargoyle"},"P17":{"creature":"mummy"},"O11":{"annotation":"letterG"},"Q11":{"creature":"zombie"},"P10":{"creature":"skeleton"},"O10":{"creature":"skeleton"},"L13":{"annotation":"letterI"},"L14":{"annotation":"letterI"},"I15":{"annotation":"letterJ"}},"narrative":"Last%20time%2C%20on%20Huntr%2Fx%20Quest%3A%0A%0AThe%20girls%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20passage%20to%20the%20underworld%2C%20in%20their%20quest%20to%20rescue%20Celine%20from%20the%20grasp%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%3A%20the%20first%20humans%20to%20walk%20into%20the%20center%20of%20demonic%20power%20in%20generations.%0A%0A---%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20Quest%206.%20%20The%20Temple%20of%20Infinite%20Abyss.%0A%0AThe%20girls%20descended%20down%20the%20worn%20stone%20spiral%20staircase%20for%20what%20felt%20like%20hours.%20%20As%20they%20did%20so%2C%20it%20felt%20as%20if%20the%20laws%20of%20physics%20itself%20were%20starting%20to%20change%3A%20small%20pebbles%20and%20debris%20levitating%20slightly%20off%20of%20the%20ground%2C%20stone%20illuminating%20the%20path%20without%20fire%20or%20electricity%2C%20and%20the%20air%20pulsing%20with%20visible%20streaks%20of%20blue%20and%20red%20magic.%0A%0AFinally%2C%20they%20reach%20a%20large%20clearing%3A%20a%20cave%20with%20walls%20and%20ceiling%20of%20dark%20red%20stone%20ten%20stories%20tall%2C%20and%20in%20the%20middle%20a%20temple%20made%20of%20the%20same%20red%20stone%20and%20dark%20mahogany%20wood.%20%20At%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20clearing%2C%20a%20crudely%20carved%20stone%20tablet%20with%20barely%20decipherable%20characters%20says%20%22Hunters%2C%20beware!%20%20You%20have%20reached%20the%20threshold%20of%20the%20underworld.%20%20The%20Honmoon%20will%20not%20protect%20you%20here.%22%0A%0ASure%20enough%2C%20when%20you%20try%20to%20spawn%20your%20weapons%20nothing%20happens.%0A%0AYou%20read%20on%3A%20%22In%20this%20demonic%20temple%2C%20I%20have%20hidden%20an%20artifact%20that%20will%20allow%20you%20to%20access%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20honmoon%20even%20in%20these%20unholy%20places.%20%20If%20you%20must%20proceed%20further%2C%20first%20retrieve%20this%20artifact.%20%20But%20be%20careful%2C%20and%20attempt%20to%20evade%20combat%20if%20possible.%20%20Somewhere%20in%20the%20temple%20you%20will%20also%20find%20the%20staircase%20leading%20deeper%20into%20the%20underworld%2C%20if%20you%20dare%20to%20encounter%20it.%20%20Good%20luck.%22%20%20It%20is%20signed%20by%20a%20hunter%20named%20Hwa-young%2C%20whose%20name%20does%20not%20sound%20familiar%20to%20you.%20%20This%20must%20have%20been%20created%20a%20very%20long%20time%20ago.%0A%0AUntil%20you%20find%20this%20artifact%2C%20you%20will%20neither%20be%20able%20to%20use%20your%20weapons%20nor%20abilities%2C%20and%20your%20attack%20power%20will%20be%201%20unless%20aided%20by%20a%20physical%20weapon.%20%20You%20stealthily%20sneak%20to%20a%20side%20entrance%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20and%20poke%20your%20head%20inside.%20%20Recover%20your%20abilities%20and%20then%20find%20your%20way%20further%20into%20the%20underworld!","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20-%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%0A%0A**A**%20-%20When%20a%20hero%20steps%20here%20and%20does%20not%20yet%20have%20their%20powers%20back%2C%20say%20*You%20can%20hear%20many%20voices%20behind%20this%20door.%20%20It%20may%20be%20safer%20to%20not%20proceed%20until%20you've%20reconnected%20with%20your%20powers.*%0A%0A**B**%20-%20When%20a%20hero%20steps%20here%20and%20does%20not%20yet%20have%20their%20powers%20back%2C%20say%20*You%20can%20hear%20the%20voice%20of%20a%20demon%20just%20around%20the%20corner.%20%20Now%20may%20be%20the%20time%20to%20turn%20back%20and%20find%20another%20way.*%0A%0A**C**%20-%20When%20a%20hero%20steps%20here%20and%20does%20not%20yet%20have%20their%20powers%20back%2C%20say%20*You%20put%20your%20ear%20to%20this%20door%2C%20and%20don't%20hear%20anything%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20%20It%20might%20be%20safe%20to%20try%20this%20one.*%0A%0A**D**%20-%20*The%20demons%20in%20this%20room%20appear%20to%20be%20sleeping.%20%20Is%20this%20some%20kind%20of%20barracks%3F*%0A%0A**E**%20-%20%20As%20you%20open%20the%20door%3A%20*You%20think%20you%20see%20a%20faint%20blue%20glow%20coming%20from%20the%20nearby%20weapon%20rack.%20%20More%20monsters%20are%20sleeping%20in%20this%20room.*%0A%0A**F**%20-%20When%20the%20first%20girl%20reaches%20the%20rack%3A%20*As%20you%20approach%20the%20weapon%20rack%2C%20the%20blue%20glow%20begins%20to%20become%20stronger.%20%20It's%20coming%20from%20a%20small%20knife%2C%20with%20a%20blue%20stone%20now%20shining%20as%20bright%20as%20daylight%20as%20you%20reach%20out%20to%20touch%20it.%20%20Upon%20touching%20it%2C%20a%20blue%20glow%20envelops%20you!%20%20You%20feel%20your%20strength%20returning.%20%20You%20attempt%20to%20take%20the%20knife%2C%20but%20it%20is%20somehow%20permanently%20attached%20to%20this%20rack.%20%20The%20other%20girls%20are%20going%20to%20need%20to%20come%20in%20and%20touch%20it%20as%20well%20to%20regain%20their%20powers.%0A%0ASuddenly%20you%20see%20the%20enemies%20in%20the%20room%20waking%20up.%20%20Defend%20yourselves!*%20%20All%20the%20monsters%20in%20the%20adjoining%20rooms%20now%20wake%20up%20and%20can%20move%20during%20Gwi-Ma's%20turn.%0A%0AThe%20girls%20will%20each%20need%20to%20stand%20next%20to%20the%20rack%20to%20regain%20their%20powers.%0A%0A**G**%20-%20When%20searching%20for%20treasure%20in%20this%20room%2C%20the%20girls%20find%20an%20ancient%20treasure%20chest%20with%20runes%20on%20it.%20%20It%20has%20a%20meteor%20trap!%20%20Place%20a%203%20x%203%20Meteor%20overlay%20on%20(G)%20and%20say%20*You%20see%20the%20silhouette%20of%20something%20large%20coming%20down%20from%20the%20ceiling.%20%20Move%20out%20of%20the%20way%20if%20you%20can!*%0A%0AAt%20the%20start%20of%20Gwi-Ma's%20next%20turn%2C%20any%20units%20standing%20on%20the%20insert%20take%203%20body%20points%20of%20damage.%0A%0AThe%20chest%20contains%20100gp%20per%20hero%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Potion%20of%20Healing.%0A%0A**H**%20-%20When%20entering%20this%20room%2C%20say%3A%20*You%20see%20a%20glowing%20tome%20on%20the%20altar.%20%20the%20words%20suddenly%20fly%20off%20of%20the%20page%20and%20surround%20you%2C%20swirling%20around%20you%20with%20glowing%20blue%20magic.*%0A%0A**I**%20-%20If%20the%20girls%20have%20not%20done%20(H)%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20attempt%20to%20open%20the%20doors%2C%20but%20they%20are%20locked.%20%20Glowing%20blue%20runes%20illuminate%20the%20door%20whenever%20you%20touch%20it.%20%20There%20must%20be%20a%20way%20to%20open%20it.*%0A%0AIf%20they%20have%20done%20(H)%2C%20say%20the%20following%20and%20then%20open%20both%20doors%3A%0A%0A*At%20a%20touch%2C%20the%20glowing%20blue%20runes%20that%20were%20surrounding%20you%20pour%20into%20the%20doors.%20%20In%20a%20flash%20of%20light%2C%20the%20doors%20are%20opened%20revealing%20the%20stairs%20down%20and%20the%20demons%20who%20were%20waiting%20for%20you%20on%20the%20other%20side!%20%20Before%20you%20stands%20an%20entire%20warband%20of%20terrifying%20Chaos%20Warriors%2C%20demons%20trained%20in%20the%20art%20of%20combat.%20%20There's%20no%20turning%20back%20now!*%0A%0AEach%20chaos%20warrior%20drops%2050gp%20per%20hero%20as%20they%20fall%2C%20200gp%20total%20once%20all%204%20are%20felled.%0A%0A**J**%20-%20When%20all%20the%20girls%20have%20reached%20the%20staircase%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20look%20at%20each%20other%20with%20a%20glance%20of%20hesitation%2C%20but%20then%20strengthen%20your%20resolve%20and%20proceed%20down%20the%20stairs.%20%20Celine%20is%20down%20here.%20%20Somewhere.%0A%0AYou%20each%20receive%20500gp%20worth%20of%20experience%20from%20conquering%20the%20Temple%20of%20Infinite%20Abyss.*","wanderingMonster":"Zombie","style":"hq-us"},{"id":"c468509e-d670-408b-a935-67183f02079e","title":"7.%20The%20Threshold%20of%20Torment","author":"","created":"2026-06-16T09:53:46.803Z","