ock"},"F24":{"annotation":"rock"},"F25":{"annotation":"rock"},"E25":{"annotation":"rock"},"E24":{"annotation":"rock"},"E23":{"annotation":"rock"},"E22":{"annotation":"rock"},"E21":{"annotation":"rock"},"E20":{"annotation":"rock"},"E19":{"annotation":"rock"},"E18":{"annotation":"rock"},"E17":{"annotation":"rock"},"F17":{"annotation":"rock"},"F16":{"annotation":"rock"},"F15":{"annotation":"rock"},"E15":{"annotation":"rock"},"E16":{"annotation":"rock"},"D16":{"annotation":"rock"},"D15":{"annotation":"rock"},"C15":{"annotation":"rock"},"B15":{"annotation":"rock"},"B16":{"annotation":"rock"},"C16":{"annotation":"rock"},"C17":{"annotation":"rock"},"B17":{"annotation":"rock"},"B18":{"annotation":"rock"},"C18":{"annotation":"rock"},"D18":{"annotation":"rock"},"D17":{"annotation":"rock"},"B19":{"annotation":"rock"},"B20":{"annotation":"rock"},"B21":{"annotation":"rock"},"B22":{"annotation":"rock"},"B23":{"annotation":"rock"},"B24":{"annotation":"rock"},"B25":{"annotation":"rock"},"C25":{"annotation":"rock"},"D25":{"annotation":"rock"},"D24":{"annotation":"rock"},"D23":{"annotation":"rock"},"D22":{"annotation":"rock"},"D21":{"annotation":"rock"},"D20":{"annotation":"rock"},"D19":{"annotation":"rock"},"C19":{"annotation":"rock"},"C20":{"annotation":"rock"},"C21":{"annotation":"rock"},"C22":{"annotation":"rock"},"C23":{"annotation":"rock"},"C24":{"annotation":"rock"},"J23":{},"S14":{"homebrew":"https://images2.imgbox.com/d3/3d/CtEjNGd8_o.jpg||19-14__","background":"homebrew_W_19-14__"}},"narrative":"The%20girls%20found%20their%20way%20to%20a%20demonic%20temple%20at%20the%20threshold%20of%20the%20underworld.%20%20Regaining%20their%20powers%20after%20being%20disconnected%20from%20the%20Honmoon%2C%20they%20ventured%20deeper%20in%20their%20quest%20to%20rescue%20Celine.%0A%0A---%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20Quest%207.%20%20The%20Threshold%20of%20Torment.%0A%0AFinally%2C%20you%20make%20your%20way%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20staircase.%20%20Making%20your%20way%20through%20a%20narrow%20passage%2C%20you%20suddenly%20find%20yourself%20in%20a%20cave%20system%20so%20large%20that%20it%20seems%20as%20if%20it's%20an%20entire%20separate%20world%20within%20the%20underworld%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20softly%20glowing%20red%20sky%20thanks%20to%20the%20unearthly%20red%20stone%20that%20covers%20the%20cavern.%20%20It%20sprawls%20in%20every%20direction%2C%20and%20lakes%20of%20lava%20dot%20the%20landscape.%20%20In%20the%20distance%2C%20you%20see%20the%20dark%20black%20stone%20of%20a%20foreboding%20fortress.%20%20You%20remember%20reading%20about%20the%20black%20stone%20fortress%20in%20the%20Chronicles%20of%20Mudang%3A%20this%20is%20Agwi%20Hwasin's%20fortress%2C%20the%20dreaded%20keep%20Agwisanseong!%0A%0AIt's%20surrounded%20by%20a%20lava%20moat%2C%20and%20you%20must%20cross%20a%20dangerous%20looking%20field%20where%20you%20will%20be%20exposed%20to%20all%20onlookers%20to%20reach%20it.%20%20You%20must%20find%20a%20way%20inside.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20-%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%20%20Immediately%20reveal%20everyone%20in%20the%20field%20and%20say%3A%0A*This%20field%20of%20ash%20is%20teeming%20with%20demons!%20%20To%20your%20dismay%2C%20they%20all%20turn%20to%20face%20you%20at%20once!%20%20This%20has%20become%20a%20fight%20for%20your%20lives!*%0A%0AOnce%20the%20fight%20is%20over%2C%20instead%20of%20pulling%20a%20treasure%20from%20the%20deck%20on%20search%2C%20say%3A%20*The%20corpses%20of%20the%20demon%20hoard%20surround%20you.%20%20Amidst%20the%20debris%2C%20you%20find%20300gp%20worth%20of%20ancient%20coins%20per%20hero%20that%20they%20must%20have%20looted%20off%20of%20some%20other%20humans%20who%20were%20unfortunate%20enough%20to%20find%20their%20way%20here.%20%20Your%20battle%20sense%20strengthens%20your%20resolve%2C%20and%20each%20of%20you%20also%20gains%20a%20permanent%20Attribute%20upgrade%20of%20your%20choice%20if%20you%20have%20an%20available%20slot%20left.%0A%0AYou've%20defeated%20the%20army%20guarding%20the%20castle%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20see%20an%20obvious%20way%20inside.%20%20The%20lava%20moat%20is%20impassible%2C%20and%20the%20drawbridge%20is%20raised.*%0A%0A**A**%20-%20*You%20come%20to%20the%20door%20of%20this%20tower%2C%20and%20see%20that%20there%20is%20a%20small%20service%20bridge%20across%20the%20moat!*%0A%0A**B**%20-%20*With%20all%20your%20bravery%2C%20you%20begin%20the%20slow%20walk%20over%20boiling%20lava%2C%20with%20only%20the%20rickety%20wood%20of%20this%20service%20bridge%20holding%20you%20up.%20%20The%20bridge%20creaks%20and%20groans%2C%20but%20holds.*%0A%0A**C**%20-%20*Finally%2C%20you%20locate%20a%20service%20entrance%20along%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20castle.%20%20Hopefully%20it%20leads%20to%20something%20promising.*%0A%0A**D**%20-%20*You%20see%20a%20table%20with%20levers%20on%20it%2C%20connected%20to%20giant%20chains.%20%20And%20several%20demons%20lying%20in%20wait!*%0A%0AWhen%20the%20heroes%20interact%20with%20the%20lever%3A%0A%0A*You%20watch%20as%20the%20chains%20move%20at%20tremendous%20speed%20once%20the%20lever%20releases%20them%2C%20and%20you%20hear%20the%20thunderous%20crash%20of%20stone%20upon%20stone!*%0A%0A(The%20drawbridge%20at%20E%20is%20now%20open.%20%20Place%20it%20once%20heroes%20get%20in%20line%20of%20sight%20of%20(E))%0A%0A**E**%20-%20If%20the%20drawbridge%20was%20opened%20with%20(D)%2C%20spawn%20the%20drawbridge%20here%20when%20a%20hero%20gets%20in%20line%20of%20sight%20of%20E%2C%20along%20with%20a%20special%20Chaos%20Warrior%20on%20it%20that%20has%20the%20following%20stats%3A%0A%0AAttack%20dice%3A%205%0ADefense%20dice%3A%205%0ABody%20Points%3A%206%0AMind%20Points%3A%208%0AMovement%3A%205%0AType%3A%20Tactical%0AManeuver%3A%20Intimidate%0ASpecial%3A%20Damage%20Minimum%20(2)%20(%22Your%20blow%20glances%20off%20of%20his%20armor%20as%20the%20glowing%20red%20energy%20condenses%20near%20the%20point%20of%20impact.%20%20You're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20hit%20harder%20to%20break%20through.%22)%0A%0ASay%3A%20*The%20drawbridge%20is%20lowered!%20%20And%20a%20horrible%20warrior%20of%20Chaos%20stands%20defending%20it.%20%20It%20is%20wrapped%20in%20a%20glowing%20red%20energy.%20%20Brace%20yourselves!*%0A%0A**F**%20-%20This%20is%20the%20ending%20point%20of%20the%20quest.%20%20Once%20a%20girl%20makes%20it%20here%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*Crossing%20the%20drawbridge%2C%20you%20make%20your%20way%20into%20the%20castle.%20%20Celine%20must%20be%20in%20here%20somewhere.%20%20You've%20beaten%20an%20entire%20army%20to%20get%20this%20far%3A%20you%20feel%20like%20nothing%20can%20stop%20you%20now.%0A%0AFor%20your%20acts%20of%20bravery%2C%20each%20hero%20gets%20600gp%20worth%20of%20experience.*","wanderingMonster":"Fimir","style":"hq-us","homebrew":["https://images2.imgbox.com/59/cb/vCZBJtMt_o.jpg||7-3__","https://images2.imgbox.com/d3/3d/CtEjNGd8_o.jpg||19-14__"]},{"id":"ca463886-94f6-4888-a601-f6ea5ca6694f","title":"8.%20The%20Battle%20of%20Agwisanseong","author":"","created":"2026-06-16T10:56:40.808Z","updated":"2026-06-25T13:48:46.004Z","layout":"defaultMap","map":{"A14":{"annotation":"letterX"},"A13":{"annotation":"letterX"},"M15":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"M12":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"A12":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"A15":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"K17":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"K10":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"I26":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"I1":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"N1":{"annotation":"letterA"},"N26":{"annotation":"letterA"},"S1":{"annotation":"letterB"},"S26":{"annotation":"letterB"},"I9":{"door":"secretdoorS"},"I18":{"door":"secretdoorS"},"H9":{"annotation":"letterB"},"H18":{"annotation":"letterB"},"E6":{"furniture":"chestN"},"F21":{"furniture":"chestN"},"G21":{"annotation":"letterC"},"F6":{"annotation":"letterC"},"G19":{"furniture":"rackS"},"H6":{"furniture":"weaponsrackW"},"S9":{"tile":"speartrap"},"S11":{"tile":"speartrap"},"S16":{"tile":"speartrap"},"S18":{"tile":"speartrap"},"Q13":{"tile":"pittrap"},"Q14":{"tile":"pittrap"},"M13":{"door":"doorN","annotation":"letterE"},"M14":{"door":"doorN","annotation":"letterE"},"N12":{"door":"doorE"},"