{"annotation":"rock"},"A2":{"annotation":"rock"},"A3":{"annotation":"rock"},"A4":{"annotation":"rock"},"A5":{"annotation":"rock"},"A6":{"annotation":"rock"},"A7":{"annotation":"rock"},"A8":{"annotation":"rock"},"A9":{"annotation":"rock"},"A10":{"annotation":"rock"},"A11":{"annotation":"rock"},"A16":{"annotation":"rock"},"A17":{"annotation":"rock"},"A18":{"annotation":"rock"},"A19":{"annotation":"rock"},"A20":{"annotation":"rock"},"A21":{"annotation":"rock"},"A22":{"annotation":"rock"},"A23":{"annotation":"rock"},"A24":{"annotation":"rock"},"A25":{"annotation":"rock"},"A26":{"annotation":"rock"},"B26":{"annotation":"rock"},"C26":{"annotation":"rock"},"D26":{"annotation":"rock"},"E26":{"annotation":"rock"},"F26":{"annotation":"rock"},"G26":{"annotation":"rock"},"H26":{"annotation":"rock"},"R9":{"door":"doorE","annotation":"letterH"},"N11":{"creature":"mummy"},"N7":{},"O10":{"furniture":"bookcaseE"},"P11":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"P12":{"creature":"abomination"},"Q9":{"tile":"speartrap"},"R8":{"tile":"speartrap"},"Q7":{"tile":"speartrap"},"R6":{"tile":"speartrap"},"P8":{"tile":"speartrap"},"P6":{"tile":"speartrap"},"O7":{"tile":"speartrap"},"O9":{"tile":"speartrap"},"N8":{"tile":"speartrap"},"N6":{"tile":"speartrap"},"P2":{"furniture":"chesttrapN"},"Q2":{"furniture":"chesttrapN"},"R2":{"furniture":"chesttrapN"},"Q3":{"annotation":"letterI"},"O2":{"door":"doorN"},"K5":{"creature":"mummy","door":"doorE"},"L9":{"door":"doorE"},"M11":{"door":"doorN","annotation":"letterK"},"M2":{"tile":"pittrap"},"M3":{"tile":"pittrap"},"M4":{"tile":"pittrap"},"M5":{"tile":"pittrap"},"K3":{"creature":"zombie"},"K4":{"creature":"skeleton"},"K2":{"creature":"skeleton"},"L3":{"annotation":"letterJ"},"H13":{"furniture":"throneN"},"H14":{"furniture":"throneN"},"I13":{"creature":"chaossorcerer"},"O5":{"door":"doorE"},"J15":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"L15":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"K16":{"creature":"abomination"},"M7":{"door":"doorE"},"J11":{"furniture":"fireplaceW"}},"narrative":"Last%20time%2C%20on%20Huntr%2Fx%20Quest%3A%0A%0AThe%20girls%20ventured%20into%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20underworld%20itself%2C%20and%20at%20the%20gates%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin's%20black%20fortress%20-%20Agwisanseong%20-%20they%20managed%20to%20defeat%20a%20small%20army%20of%20demonic%20forces%20and%20fight%20their%20way%20through%20the%20front%20door.%20%20Celine%20and%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20must%20be%20somewhere%20inside.%0A%0A---%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20quest%208%3A%20The%20Battle%20of%20Agwisanseong.%0A%0AYou%20find%20yourselves%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20massive%20iron%20gates%2C%20and%20the%20entryway%20is%20surprisingly%20empty.%20%20Where%20is%20everyone%3F%0A%0AOne%20way%20or%20another%2C%20you%20must%20confront%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20and%20save%20Celine.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20-%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%0A%0A**A**%20-%20When%20one%20of%20the%20girls%20reach%20either%20of%20these%20points%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*Suddenly%20you%20hear%20the%20thundering%20rush%20of%20footsteps.%20%20It%20was%20a%20trap!*%0A%0AAt%20each%20(B)%20location%20(4%20of%20them)%2C%20spawn%203%20goblins%2C%203%20orcs%2C%20and%201%20fimir%2C%20in%20that%20order%2C%20spawning%20each%20a%20square%20further%20away%20from%20the%20closest%20(A)%20location.%20%20These%20combined%20all%20count%20as%20a%20single%20encounter%20together%20and%20not%20wandering%20monsters.%20%20The%20secret%20doors%20where%20two%20of%20the%20(B)%20locations%20exist%20automatically%20open.%20%20The%20monsters%20now%20take%20their%20turn%20*immediately*%20as%20well%20as%20preceding%20as%20normal%20on%20Gwi-Ma's%20next%20turn.%0A%0A**B**%20-%20These%20are%20locations%20where%20the%20monsters%20who%20laid%20the%20trap%20in%20(A)%20are%20spawned.%0A%0A**C**%20-%20Heroes%20who%20explore%20the%20rooms%20where%20the%20ambushers%20came%20from%20will%20discover%20100gp%20in%20each%20of%20the%20treasure%20chests.%0A%0A**D**%20-%20When%20a%20hero%20tries%20to%20open%20this%20door%2C%20say%3A%20*This%20sturdy%20iron%20door%20appears%20to%20be%20locked.%20%20No%20amount%20of%20pulling%20at%20or%20attacking%20it%20seems%20to%20budge%20it%20in%20the%20least.%20%20There%20is%20a%20large%20keyhole%2C%20but%20none%20of%20you%20can%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20pick%20it.*%0A%0AIf%20the%20heroes%20defeated%20the%20Hand%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20at%20(L)%2C%20they%20have%20the%20key%20and%20can%20unlock%20the%20door%2C%20at%20which%20point%20the%20quest%20ends.%20%20Say%3A%0A%0A*You%20unlock%20and%20push%20at%20the%20massive%20iron%20door%2C%20and%20it%20slowly%20slides%20open%20revealing%20a%20long%20hallway%20of%20prison%20cells.%20%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20wasn't%20here%2C%20but%20hopefully%20he%20left%20Celine%20behind.%20%20Wherever%20he%20went.%0A%0AFor%20your%20heroism%2C%20you%20each%20gain%20400gp%20worth%20of%20experience.*%0A%0A**E**%20-%20When%20a%20hero%20tries%20to%20open%20this%20door%2C%20say%3A%20*You%20reach%20for%20the%20door%20handle%2C%20when%20suddenly%20you%20hear%20a%20sound%20like%20a%20jet%20engine%20down%20the%20hall!%20%20You%20look%20and%20see%20the%20hallway%20appearing%20to%20light%20up%20with%20an%20enormous%20ball%20of%20fire!*%0A%0APlace%20two%20skull%20tiles%20on%20(F)%20to%20indicate%20where%20the%20fire%20is%20located.%20%20Every%20turn%2C%20they%20will%20move%20up%20one%20space%20until%20they%20hit%20the%20doors%20at%20(E).%20%20Any%20hero%20who%20enters%20or%20occupies%20its%20space%20at%20the%20start%20of%20their%20turn%20takes%203%20body%20points%20of%20damage.%0A%0ASubsequent%20attempts%20to%20open%20these%20doors%20result%20in%20the%20same%20fireball%20being%20generated.%0A%0A**F**%20-%20This%20is%20where%20the%20fireball%20in%20(E)%20is%20generated%20when%20it%20triggers.%0A%0A**G**%20-%20When%20a%20hero%20tries%20to%20open%20this%20door%2C%20say%3A%20*This%20door%20is%20made%20of%20solid%20iron%2C%20but%20the%20hinges%20appear%20to%20be%20rusty.%20%20You%20might%20be%20able%20to%20break%20it%20down%20with%20an%20assisted%20body%20check!*%0A%0AIf%20the%20hero%20succeeds%20in%20the%20check%2C%20the%20door%20is%20opened.%20%20If%20not%2C%20the%20door%20remains%20closed%20and%20that%20hero%20cannot%20attempt%20again%20until%20their%20next%20turn.%0A%0A**H**%20-%20Ask%20each%20of%20the%20heroes%20to%20make%20an%20unassisted%20Mind%20check.%20%20If%20any%20succeeds%2C%20tell%20them%3A%20*You%20observe%20that%20there's%20an%20unusual%20pattern%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20this%20room%2C%20where%20some%20of%20the%20floor%20tiles%20appear%20strangely%20loose.%20%20It%20reminds%20you%20of%20a%20chess%20board.*%0A%0A**I**%20-%20If%20the%20heroes%20walk%20up%20to%20any%20of%20these%20chests%20and%20open%20them%2C%20each%20will%20set%20off%20a%20fire%20trap%20that%20deals%201%20damage%20to%20the%20opener%20and%20spawn%20a%20wandering%20monster%20demon%20directly%20behind%20them%3A%20that%20demon%20gets%20a%20free%20attack%20against%20the%20chest%20opener.%20%20Each%20chest%20contains%20100gp.%0A%0A**J**%20-%20*When%20you%20open%20the%20door%2C%20you%20notice%20that%20the%20monsters%20don't%20seem%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20you.*%20%20Ask%20each%20hero%20to%20make%20an%20unassisted%20mind%20check.%20%20If%20any%20succeeds%2C%20tell%20them%20that%20you%20see%20the%20crude%20trap%20they've%20laid%20out%20and%20reveal%20each%20of%20the%20pit%20traps%20in%20the%20room.%20%20The%20monsters%20will%20only%20attack%20once%20the%20heroes%20are%20either%20in%20the%20pit%20or%20have%20crossed%20it%2C%20and%20will%20not%20cross%20the%20pit%20willingly.%0A%0A**K**%20-%20When%20the%20hero%20goes%20to%20open%20the%20door%3A%20*You%20carefully%20reach%20out%20for%20the%20door%2C%20wondering%20what%20diabolical%20trap%20is%20laid%20for%20you%20next.%20%20But%20instead%2C%20the%20door%20slides%20open%20freely.%20%20You%20see%20before%20you%20the%20throne%20room%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%2C%20but%20the%20demon%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found.%20%20Instead%2C%20a%20large%20and%20intimidating%20demon%20sits%20on%20the%20throne%20in%20his%20place%2C%20surrounded%20by%20underlings.%20%20The%20surface%20of%20his%20skin%20is%20swirling%20with%20blue%20energy.%20%20%22Greetingsss%2C%20mortals.%22%20%20It%20hisses%20out%20between%20clenched%20teeth.%20%20%22I%20am%20the%20right%20hand%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%2C%20and%20you%20did%20well%20to%20survive%20thus%20far.%20%20But%20you%20will%20go%20no%20further!%22%0A%0AThe%20Right%20hand%20has%20the%20following%20stats%3A%0AAttack%20Dice%3A%202%2C%20Multi-attack%20(4)%20(%22it%20scratches%20at%20you%20with%20impossibly%20fast%20claws!%22)%0ADefense%20Dice%3A%202%0ABody%20Points%3A%207%0AMind%20Points%3A%206%0AType%3A%20Tactical%0AManeuver%3A%20Teleport%0ASpecial%3A%20Damage%20Limit%20(2)%20(%22The%20swirling%20blue%20energy%20surrounding%20him%20seems%20to%20limit%20the%20amount%20of%20damage%20he%20can%20take%20in%20a%20single%20blow!%22)%0A%0AThe%20Right%20hand%20gets%20to%20cast%20Ball%20of%20Flame%20immediately%20at%20whoever%20opened%20the%20door.%0A%0AWhen%20they%20search%20the%20room%2C%20instead%20of%20pulling%20a%20treasure%20card%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20check%20the%20corpse%20of%20the%20right%20hand%20for%20anything%20valuable.%20%20You%20find%20a%20heavy%20iron%20key.%20%20Did%20you%20see%20a%20door%20earlier%20that%20might%20fit%20this%3F%20%20You%20also%20find%20300gp%20per%20hero%20stuffed%20under%20the%20seat%20cushions%20of%20the%20throne.%20%20With%20that%20done%2C%20you%20have%20found%20neither%20Celine%20nor%20Agwi%20Hwasin.%20%20Perhaps%20this%20key%20will%20lead%20to%20one%20of%20them%2C%20if%20you%20can%20find%20the%20door%20into%20which%20it%20fits.*%0A%0AThe%20heroes%20must%20now%20backtrack%20to%20(D)%20to%20open%20the%20iron%20door%20and%20enter%20the%20dungeons.","wanderingMonster":"Fimir","style":"hq-us"},{"id":"de4595d6-177a-46d3-87f5-b394e56639a8","title":"9.%20The%20Dungeons%20of%20Agwisanseong","author":"","created":"2026-06-16T13:00:58.734Z","updated":"2026-06-25T13:50:23.736Z","layout":"defaultMap","map":{"K1":{"tile":"block