4"}},"narrative":"%22Last%20time%2C%20on%20Huntr%2Fx%20Quest%22%3A%0A%0AThe%20girls%20rescued%20Celine%20from%20the%20maw%20of%20the%20underworld%20itself%20and%20made%20a%20desperate%20flight%20to%20safety%2C%20but%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20evaded%20them.%20%20Once%20they%20got%20to%20the%20surface%2C%20they%20began%20to%20plan%20how%20to%20lure%20him%20out%20from%20hiding%20for%20a%20final%20confrontation.%0A%0A---%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20quest%2010%3A%20Diss%20Track.%0A%0ABobby%2C%20Celine%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20sat%20in%20the%20girl's%20apartment%20planning%20their%20next%20move%20carefully.%20%20Bobby%20proposed%20that%20they%20create%20a%20new%20diss%20track%20and%20premiere%20it%20at%20the%20stadium%20in%20front%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20their%20adoring%20fans%3A%20perhaps%20dissing%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20would%20lure%20him%20out%20of%20hiding%3F%0A%0AEveryone%20agreed%20that%20was%20a%20great%20idea%2C%20so%20they%20made%20the%20arrangements.%20%20Celine%20prepared%20four%20blue%20runes%20at%20the%20corners%20of%20the%20stage.%20%20%22Remember%20girls%2C%20if%20you%20step%20onto%20one%20of%20these%20runes%2C%20your%20Encounter%20and%20Rest%20abilities%20will%20recharge%20automatically.%20%20You%20might%20need%20it!%22%20%20%0A%0AAnd%20now%20here%20you%20are%2C%20at%20the%20Jamsil%20Indoor%20Stadium%2C%20surrounded%20by%20fans%20on%20all%20sides%2C%20preparing%20to%20debut%20your%20new%20hit%20single%20%22Agwi%20Hwasin%20Smells%20Like%20Old%20Goat%20Farts%22.%0A%0AAs%20you%20reach%20the%20center%20of%20the%20circular%20stage%2C%20you%20can%20hear%20the%20screams%20of%20the%20crowd%20as%20they%20see%20hordes%20of%20demons%20pouring%20in%20from%20the%20aisles%20towards%20you.%20%20It%20looks%20like%20the%20plan%20worked!%20%20Defend%20the%20stage%20until%20the%20demonic%20forces%20have%20exhausted%20themselves%20and%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20is%20forced%20to%20reveal%20himself.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7X%20-%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%0A%0ASay%20the%20following%3A%20*The%20demons%20charge%20the%20stage%2C%20but%20you're%20ready%20for%20them.%20%20Give%20it%20everything%20you've%20got.%20%20Remember%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20you%20must%20remain%20on%20the%20stage%20so%20that%20the%20performance%20continues.%20%20If%20none%20of%20the%20girls%20are%20on%20the%20central%20stage%20at%20the%20start%20of%20Gwi-Ma's%20turn%2C%20(the%20gray%20and%20black%20octagon%20squares%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20map)%2C%20the%20mission%20ends%20in%20a%20failure%20and%20will%20have%20to%20be%20attempted%20again.*%0A%0ASpawn%20Goblins%20at%20each%20B%20location.%20%20They%20immediately%20get%20to%20take%20their%20move%20and%20action%20if%20possible.%0A%0APlace%203%20skull%20tokens%20on%20the%20table%20in%20a%20visible%20location%2C%20let%20the%20girls%20know%20that%20this%20is%20the%20countdown%20before%20more%20demons%20spawn.%0A%0AAt%20the%20start%20of%20every%20Gwi-Ma%20round%2C%20remove%20a%20skull%20token.%20%20If%20you%20cannot%2C%20then%20spawn%20the%20next%20of%20the%20following%20waves%20from%20the%20B%20locations%20and%20place%203%20skull%20tokens%20back%20on%20the%20board%2C%20until%20there%20are%20no%20more%20waves%20to%20spawn.%0A%0A-%206%20Skeletons%0A-%206%20Orcs%0A-%203%20Fimirs%2C%202%20Zombies%2C%201%20Mummy%0A-%206%20Chaos%20Warriors%0A-%202%20Gargoyles%2C%204%20Orcs%0A-%201%20Chaos%20Sorcerer%20%22The%20Last%20Disciple%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%22%0A%0AIf%20you%20don't%20have%20enough%20units%20to%20spawn%20all%20of%20them%2C%20spawn%20the%20next%20available%20unit%20of%20similar%20or%20lesser%20power%20in%20the%20Enemy%20Type%20scale%20(Boss%2C%20High%2C%20Mid%20etc...).%0A%0AThen%20the%20Last%20Disciple%20spawns%2C%20say%20*You've%20made%20him%20angry!%20%20He%20has%20sent%20his%20last%20and%20most%20powerful%20disciple%20after%20you.%20%20Brace%20yourselves!*%20%20He%20has%20the%20following%20stats%3A%0A%0AAttack%20Dice%3A%203%2C%20with%202%20additional%20guaranteed%20skull%0ADefense%20Dice%3A%204%0ABody%20Points%3A%2015%0AMind%20Points%3A%2010%0AType%3A%20Tactical%0ASpecial%3A%20At%20the%20start%20of%20his%20turn%2C%20roll%20a%20single%20red%20dice.%20%20Place%20a%203%20x%203%20meteor%20overlay%20on%20the%20location%20matching%20that%20number%2C%20and%20then%20say%20*A%20flaming%20meteor%20somehow%20appears%20overhead!%20%20Watch%20the%20shadow%20and%20keep%20away%20from%20where%20it%20lands!*%20%20Any%20units%20other%20than%20The%20Last%20Disciple%20who%20are%20within%20the%203%20x%203%20meteor%20at%20the%20start%20of%20Gwi-Ma's%20next%20turn%20are%20hit%20for%202%20Body%20Points%20of%20damage.%0A%0AWhen%20the%20last%20enemy%20is%20defeated%2C%20say%20*As%20the%20last%20demon%20vanishes%20in%20a%20puff%20of%20smoke%20and%20ash%2C%20you%20hear%20the%20thunderous%20roar%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20himself.%20%20With%20a%20violent%20burst%20of%20lightning%2C%20the%20roof%20is%20torn%20asunder.%20%20People%20begin%20to%20flee%20as%20large%20chunks%20of%20concrete%20crash%20onto%20the%20stage%20around%20you%2C%20but%20you%20look%20up%20with%20eyes%20squinted%20in%20resolve.%20%20As%20the%20dust%20clears%2C%20you%20see%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20standing%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20ruined%20rooftop.%20%22You%20have%20played%20with%20my%20useless%20minions%20long%20enough.%20%20Come%20to%20the%20rooftop%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20you%20the%20quick%20death%20you%20deserve!%22%0A%0AYou%20gain%201000gp%20of%20experience%20from%20the%20intense%20battle.%20%20Grasping%20your%20weapon%20in%20hand%2C%20you%20make%20your%20way%20off%20the%20stage%20and%20begin%20the%20long%20climb%20to%20the%20ruined%20rooftop%20of%20the%20stadium%20for%20a%20final%20confrontation.*%0A%0AA%20-%20If%20a%20girl%20ends%20their%20turn%20on%20this%20square%2C%20their%20Encounter%20and%20Rest%20abilities%20will%20be%20replenished.%0A%0AB%20-%20These%20are%20the%20tiles%20from%20which%20monsters%20will%20spawn.%0A%0AC%20-%20Stand%20the%20chest%20on%20its%20side%20so%20it%20sort%20of%20looks%20as%20close%20to%20a%20refrigerator%20as%20it%20can%20get.%20%20When%20you%20interact%20with%20the%20chest%3A%20*Somehow%20amidst%20the%20battle%2C%20you%20found%20time%20to%20head%20back%20to%20the%20green%20room.%20%20How%20did%20you%20even%20manage%20to%20do%20this%3F%20%20Bobby%20left%20a%20Potion%20of%20Concentrated%20Honmoon%20in%20the%20mini%20fridge%20for%20you%20to%20enjoy%20after%20the%20concert%2C%20and%20300gp%20per%20hero.%20%20You%20take%20it.*","wanderingMonster":"","style":"hq-us","homebrew":["https://images2.imgbox.com/c6/71/Bs4ly6Qo_o.png||8-7__"]},{"id":"71aea5fa-9fe4-4951-b682-836e0eaf5b01","title":"11.%20Takedown%2C%20Phase%201","author":"","created":"2026-06-16T14:38:21.238Z","updated":"2026-06-17T21:00:34.479Z","layout":"blankMap","map":{"S1":{"homebrew":"https://images2.imgbox.com/cb/d5/CSnOSZgD_o.jpg||26-19__","background":"homebrew_N_26-19__"},"H21":{"annotation":"letterA"},"A2":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A8":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A24":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A12":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A6":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A10":{"annotation":"letterB"},"C2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"Q2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"O2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"M2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"K3":{"annotation":"letterX"},"K2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"I2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"G2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"E2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"A4":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A14":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A16":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A18":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A20":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A22":{"annotation":"letterB"}},"narrative":"%22Last%20time%2C%20on%20Huntr%2Fx%20Quest%22%3A%0A%0AThe%20girls%20set%20a%20trap%20for%20Agwi%20Hwasin%2C%20confronting%20him%20on%20the%20stage%20of%20the%20Jamsil%20Indoor%20Stadium.%20%20Defeating%20all%20of%20his%20minions%2C%20Agwi%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20show%20himself.%20%20In%20an%20act%20of%20brutal%20force%2C%20he%20sundered%20the%20rooftop%20of%20the%20stadium%20and%20issued%20his%20challenge%20to%20the%20girls.%20%20One%20last%20fight%2C%20here%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ruined%20stadium.%0A%0A---%0A%0ANow%20heroes%2C%20prepare%20yourselves%20for%20quest%2011%3A%20Takedown.%0A%0AAs%20you%20emerge%20onto%20what's%20left%20of%20the%20rooftop%2C%20you%20can%20see%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20himself%2C%20hovering%20a%20foot%20or%20so%20above%20on%20the%20far%20side%20of%20the%20twisted%20metal%20and%20fractured%20concrete.%20%20His%20voice%20thunders%20in%20your%20chest.%20%20%22Ah%2C%20so%20you%20came%20after%20all%2C%20to%20face%20your%20inevitable%20death.%20%20Not%20even%20the%20Honmoon%20will%20save%20you%20-%20or%20any%20of%20these%20pathetic%20humans%20-%20from%20my%20malice%20made%20manifest.%22%0A%0AFar%20below%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20the%20surge%20of%20hope%20from%20the%20crowd%20as%20they%20look%20up%20and%20see%20you%20bracing%20for%20the%20final%20confrontation.%20%20It's%20now%20or%20never%2C%20and%20far%20below%20are%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20lives%20who%20depend%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20this%20battle.%20%20This%20must%20be%20the%20end%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%2C%20for%20their%20sake.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7At%20the%20start%20of%20the%20level%2C%20place%20three%20skull%20tiles%20in%20front%20of%20you%20to%20represent%20the%20three%20boss%20phases%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin.%20%20Then%20place%20Agwi%20at%20marker%20A.%0A%0A**X**%20-%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*You%20can%20see%20the%20ruined%20fragments%20of%20rooftop%2C%20hanging%20on%20by%20still-remaining%20walls%20and%20pillars%20underneath.%20%20Looking%20down%20from%20the%20light-colored%20tiles%2C%20you%20know%20you%20wouldn't%20survive%20a%20fall.%20%20The%20crowds%20of%20people%20look%20like%20clouds%20of%20tiny%20wavering%20dots%20far%20below.%20%20%0A%0AYou%20think%20you%20could%20jump%20across%20a%20single%20square%20of%20darker%20colored%20tiles%20-%20or%20maybe%20two%20if%20you%20took%20a%20big%20risk%20-%20but%20if%20it%20was%20any%20further%20you%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20make%20it.%20%20If%20you%20have%20available%20movement%20you%20can%20do%20such%20a%20jump%20as%20part%20of%20it%2C%20but%20you%20must%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20other%20side%20with%20your%20movement%20points%2C%20and%20if%20you%20jump%20across%20a%20gap%20of%202%20tiles%20you%20must%20make%20an%20unassisted%20Body%20Check.%20%20Failure%20will%20mean%20that%20you%20barely%20grab%20the%20edge%20on%20the%20other%20side%3A%20your%20turn%20ends%20immediately%20and%20you%20are%20Immobilized%20on%20your%20next%20turn%20as%20you%20try%20to%20get%20back%20on%20your%20feet.*%0A%0AHave%20the%20group%20make%20an%20assisted%20Mind%20Check%20together.%20%20If%20they%20succeed%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20notice%20that%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20is%20glowing%20with%20a%20familiar%20kind%20of%20swirling%20blue%20magic%3A%20you%20remember%20seeing%20enemies%20that%20glow%20in%20that%20way%20being%20able%20to%20limit%20the%20amount%20of%20damage%20they%20take%20from%20a%20single%20attack.*%0A%0ARefer%20to%20the%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20Guide%2C%20Phase%201%20for%20his%20stats%20and%20moves.%0A%0AWhen%20this%20phase%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20reaches%200%20hit%20points%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*You%20finally%20see%20the%20demon%20wince%20in%20pain%20as%20its%20blue%20pulsing%20energy%20dissipates.%20%20He%20shakes%20his%20head%2C%20and%20disappears%20in%20a%20cloud%20of%20black%20smoke.%0A%0AThe%20crowd%2C%20far%20below%2C%20roars%20in%20approval.%20%20The%20cheers%20fill%20the%20midnight%20air%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20the%20Honmoon%20pulse%20a%20vibrant%20blue%20in%20recognition.%20%20You%20regain%20all%20expended%20abilities%2C%20and%20your%20body%20points%20are%20restored%20to%20full.*%0A%0ARemove%20one%20skull%20marker%2C%20and%20while%20leaving%20all%20current%20monsters%20and%20heroes%20on%20the%20board%20in%20place%2C%20proceed%20to%20the%20%22Takedown%2C%20Phase%202%22%20quest%20where%20this%20multi-phase%20quest%20will%20continue.%0A%0A**A**%20-%20%20The%20starting%20location%20for%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20during%20this%20phase.%0A%0A**B**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20top%20to%20bottom%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**C**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20top%20to%20bottom%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**D**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20left%20to%20right%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**E**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20left%20to%20right%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A%0A%0A","wanderingMonster":"","style":"hq-us","homebrew":["https://images2.imgbox.com/cb/d5/CSnOSZgD_o.jpg||26-19__"]},{"id":"3820d6fa-956a-47a8-befe-9f427f69b06c","title":"11.%20Takedown%2C%20Phase%202","author":"","created":"2026-06-16T21:30:00.110Z","updated":"2026-06-19T12:30:52.937Z","layout":"blankMap","map":{"S1":{"homebrew":"https://images2.imgbox.com/cb/d5/CSnOSZgD_o.jpg||26-19__","background":"homebrew_N_26-19__"},"G6":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE","homebrew":"https://images2.imgbox.com/2b/b0/YFndYyHM_o.png||6-4__","background":"homebrew_N_6-4__"},"G7":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"G8":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"G9":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"H6":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"H7":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"H8":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"H9":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"K22":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"L22":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"L21":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"K21":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"K20":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"L20":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"K19":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"L19":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"I12":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"I13":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"I14":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"I15":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"J15":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"J14":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"J13":{"annotation":"letterA"},"J12":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"G24":{"annotation":"letterF"},"E18":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"E17":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"E16":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"E15":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"F18":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"F17":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"F16":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"F15":{"annotation":"fancyarrowW"},"M8":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"M9":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"M10":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"M11":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"N8":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"N9":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"N10":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"N11":{"annotation":"fancyarrowE"},"A2":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A4":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A6":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A8":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A10":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A12":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A14":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A16":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A18":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A20":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A22":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A24":{"annotation":"letterC"},"C2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"E2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"G2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"I2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"K2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"M2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"O2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"Q2":{"annotation":"letterD"}},"narrative":"","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7IMPORTANT%3A%20This%20is%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20quest%2C%20all%20surviving%20units%20from%20Takedown%20Phase%201%20should%20remain%20in%20their%20identical%20spots%20for%20Phase%202.%0A%0APlace%20the%202%20x%204%20energy-wrapped%20platform%20overlays%20in%20the%202%20x%204%20locations%20marked%20with%20the%20arrows.%20%20These%20arrows%20indicate%20the%20platform's%20initial%20direction.%0A%0AEvery%20Gwi-Ma%20turn%20before%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20activates%2C%20move%20these%20platforms%20and%20all%20occupants%20one%20space%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20arrows.%20%20If%20the%20platform%20makes%20contact%20with%20another%20hard%20surface%2C%20instead%20begin%20to%20travel%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction.%20%20Repeat%20this%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20activity.%0A%0AOn%20the%20middle%202%20x%204%20platform%2C%20spawn%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20in%20space%20(A).%20%20Agwi%2C%20despite%20thematically%20%22floating%22%2C%20will%20follow%20this%20platform%20as%20it%20moves%2C%20staying%20at%20this%20position.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*Agwi%20Hwasin%20suddenly%20reappears%20hovering%20far%20above%20the%20arena.%20%20He%20raises%20his%20arms%2C%20and%20three%20massive%20chunks%20of%20the%20rooftop%20become%20enwrapped%20in%20energy%20and%20drift%20up%20to%20the%20level%20of%20the%20still-standing%20remnants.%20%20They%20begin%20to%20drift%20slowly%20back%20and%20forth%20across%20the%20void.%20%20Agwi%20floats%20down%20to%20the%20center%20platform.%0A%0AMake%20another%20Mind%20check.*%0A%0AOn%20a%20successful%20check%2C%20say%3A%20*You%20notice%20that%20he%20now%20is%20glowing%20red%3A%20a%20color%20that%20you've%20seen%20before%20indicates%20he%20has%20some%20sort%20of%20energy%20plating%20that%20ensures%20damage%20below%20a%20minimum%20threshold%20is%20ignored.%20%20You're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20hit%20him%20heavy%2C%20girls.*%0A%0ARefer%20to%20the%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20Guide%2C%20Phase%202%20for%20his%20stats%20and%20moves.%0A%0AWhen%20this%20phase%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20reaches%200%20hit%20points%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*Again%2C%20the%20demon%20winces%20in%20pain%2C%20and%20his%20red%20energy%20shield%20dissipates%20into%20the%20air.%20%20His%20eyes%20narrow%2C%20and%20he%20shouts%20angrily.%20%22ENOUGH!%20%20This%20witless%20crowd%20below%20will%20witness%20my%20true%20power%2C%20and%20come%20to%20serve%20ME!%22%20%20He%20raises%20both%20his%20arms%20into%20the%20air%20and%20thick%20purple%20smoke%20fills%20the%20stadium%20and%20surrounding%20areas.%20%20It%20tastes%20bitter%20-%20suffocating%20-%20and%20the%20girls%20stagger%20as%20they%20begin%20to%20choke%20on%20it.%0A%0AFor%20a%20moment%2C%20you%20hear%20panic%20in%20the%20crowd%20below.%20%20But%20then%20something%20different.%20%20Singing.%20%20%0A%0AAs%20the%20crowd%20defies%20the%20purple%20smoke%20meant%20to%20corrupt%20them%20into%20demons%2C%20the%20honmoon%20pulses%20in%20a%20vibrant%20flash%20and%20expels%20the%20smoke%20in%20a%20single%20burst.%20%20The%20girls%20scramble%20back%20to%20their%20feet.%0A%0AAgwi%20Hwasin%20cries%20out%20in%20unbridled%20rage%2C%20and%20once%20again%20he%20disappears%20in%20a%20cloud%20of%20smoke.%20%20As%20he%20does%20so%2C%20everyone%20on%20the%20floating%20platforms%20finds%20themselves%20standing%20on%20firm%20rooftop%20once%20more%2C%20just%20in%20time%20to%20watch%20the%20platforms%20collapse%20back%20to%20the%20ground%20with%20a%20thunderous%20jolt%20that%20shakes%20the%20earth.%0A%0AFar%20below%2C%20the%20crowd%20bursts%20into%20a%20frenzy%20of%20cheering%20and%20celebration.%20%20It%20is%20nearly%20sunrise%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20the%20Honmoon%20pulse%20a%20vibrant%20blue%20glow%20that%20amplifies%20the%20slowly%20growing%20hue%20of%20pre-dawn.%20%20You%20regain%20all%20expended%20abilities%2C%20and%20your%20body%20points%20are%20restored%20to%20full.*%0A%0ARemove%20one%20skull%20marker%2C%20and%20while%20leaving%20all%20current%20monsters%20and%20heroes%20on%20the%20board%20in%20place%2C%20proceed%20to%20the%20%22Takedown%2C%20Phase%203%22%20quest%20where%20this%20multi-phase%20quest%20will%20reach%20its%20finale.%0A%0A**A**%20-%20%20The%20starting%20location%20for%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20during%20this%20phase.%0A%0A**B**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20top%20to%20bottom%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**C**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20top%20to%20bottom%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**D**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20left%20to%20right%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**E**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20left%20to%20right%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**F**%20-%20After%20this%20phase%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20is%20defeated%2C%20all%20surviving%20units%20on%20floating%20platforms%20are%20teleported%20at%20and%20around%20F%2C%20clockwise%20in%20turn%20order.","wanderingMonster":"","style":"hq-us","homebrew":["https://images2.imgbox.com/cb/d5/CSnOSZgD_o.jpg||26-19__","https://images2.imgbox.com/2b/b0/YFndYyHM_o.png||6-4__"]},{"id":"8db40607-4958-45ca-8ed9-81ef24e6fbba","title":"11.%20Takedown%2C%20Phase%203","author":"","created":"2026-06-16T21:30:13.773Z","updated":"2026-06-18T09:17:42.886Z","layout":"blankMap","map":{"E7":{"annotation":"letterX"},"E8":{},"E18":{"annotation":"letterX"},"M18":{"annotation":"letterX"},"M7":{"annotation":"letterX"},"S1":{"homebrew":"https://images2.imgbox.com/c6/ea/q7qV51Bo_o.jpg||26-19__","background":"homebrew_N_26-19__"},"A2":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A4":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A6":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A8":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A10":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A12":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A14":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A16":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A18":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A20":{"annotation":"letterC"},"A22":{"annotation":"letterB"},"A24":{"annotation":"letterC"},"C2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"E2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"G2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"I2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"K2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"M2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"O2":{"annotation":"letterE"},"Q2":{"annotation":"letterD"},"H13":{"annotation":"letterA"}},"narrative":"","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7IMPORTANT%3A%20This%20is%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20quest%2C%20all%20surviving%20units%20from%20Takedown%20Phase%202%20should%20remain%20in%20their%20identical%20spots%20for%20Phase%203.%0A%0APlace%20the%20Phase%203%20overlay%20on%20top%20of%20the%20Phase%201%20overlay.%20%20The%20corners%20of%20the%20overlay%20should%20match%20the%20positions%20marked%20with%20%22X%22%20to%20create%20the%20combined%20image%20seen%20in%20the%20quest%20image%20above.%0A%0AOn%20the%20position%20marked%20by%20(A)%2C%20spawn%20Agwi%20Hwasin.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*Agwi%20Hwasin%20reappears%20once%20more%20hovering%20far%20above%20the%20arena.%20%20He%20again%20raises%20his%20arms%2C%20and%20more%20massive%20chunks%20of%20the%20rooftop%20drift%20upward%2C%20this%20time%20taking%20fixed%20positions%20among%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20rooftop.%20%20Agwi%20floats%20down%20to%20the%20center%20platform%20and%20howls%20at%20you%2C%20his%20eyes%20filled%20with%20uncontained%20and%20desperate%20rage.%20%20%22WHY.%20%20WON'T.%20%20YOU.%20%20DIE!!!!%22%0A%0AMake%20another%20Mind%20check.*%0A%0AOn%20a%20successful%20check%2C%20say%3A%20*He%20seems%20to%20have%20lost%20all%20of%20his%20defenses.%20%20Now%20is%20the%20time%20to%20hit%20him%20with%20everything%20you've%20got!*%0A%0ARefer%20to%20the%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20Guide%2C%20Phase%203%20for%20his%20stats%20and%20moves.%0A%0AWhen%20this%20phase%20of%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20reaches%200%20hit%20points%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*As%20your%20blade%20pierces%20the%20demon's%20form%2C%20something%20unexpected%20happens.%20%20You%20can%20see%20daylight%20from%20the%20eastern%20sunrise%20coming%20through%20the%20wound.%20%20Agwi's%20expression%20of%20rage%20turns%20to%20shock%2C%20and%20he%20looks%20down%20at%20the%20gaping%20hole%20in%20his%20form%20just%20in%20time%20to%20crumble%20into%20countless%20shards%20of%20dust%20at%20your%20feet.%20%20%22How%20did%20you...%22%20the%20creature%20mouths%2C%20but%20he%20turns%20to%20ash%20before%20sound%20can%20escape%20his%20dying%20lips.*%0A%0ARemove%20the%20final%20skull%20marker.%0A%0ASay%3A%20*As%20the%20platforms%20under%20your%20feet%20lose%20their%20magical%20flotation%2C%20you%20barely%20scramble%20to%20safety%20and%20make%20a%20flying%20leap%20for%20the%20nearest%20rooftop%20remnant.%20%20Your%20friends%20help%20you%20to%20your%20feet%2C%20and%20you%20watch%20the%20sunrise%20together%20as%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20screaming%20fans%20cheer%20your%20final%20and%20hard-fought%20victory.%20%20All%20heroes%20are%20restored%20to%20full%20health.%20%20Congratulations%3A%20you're%20a%20super%20star.%20%20And%20your%20career%20has%20only%20just%20begun.%0A%0AThe%20honmoon%20pulses%20with%20renewed%20energy%2C%20and%20the%20clear%20golden%20dawn%20presents%20a%20world%20filled%20with%20hope%20amidst%20the%20rubble.%20%20The%20world%20is%20safe%20once%20more.%20%20For%20now.%0A%0ATHE%20END.*%0A%0A**A**%20-%20%20The%20starting%20location%20for%20Agwi%20Hwasin%20during%20this%20phase.%0A%0A**B**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20top%20to%20bottom%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**C**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20top%20to%20bottom%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**D**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20left%20to%20right%20from%20this%20point.%0A%0A**E**%20-%20Starting%20points%20for%20Agwi's%20Wall%20of%20Malice%20attack%2C%20left%20to%20right%20from%20this%20point.","wanderingMonster":"","style":"hq-us","homebrew":["https://images2.imgbox.com/cb/d5/CSnOSZgD_o.jpg||26-19__","https://images2.imgbox.com/f3/20/DFewCmyo_o.jpg||13-9__","https://images2.imgbox.com/c6/ea/q7qV51Bo_o.jpg||26-19__"]},{"id":"59b61e0c-238e-4351-8136-9eef1a31e005","title":"0.%20Training%20Day","author":"","created":"2026-06-20T16:54:19.827Z","updated":"2026-06-25T13:28:17.097Z","layout":"defaultMap","map":{"A13":{"tile":"blockedwalldoubleN"},"J1":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"A1":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterX"},"B11":{"door":"doorN","annotation":"letterA"},"F9":{"door":"doorE"},"D6":{"door":"doorS"},"F10":{"annotation":"letterB"},"E6":{"annotation":"letterC"},"C5":{"door":"doorE"},"C6":{"annotation":"letterD"},"D3":{"door":"doorS","annotation":"letterE"},"I3":{"door":"doorS"},"J5":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"K3":{"door":"doorN","annotation":"letterF"},"N3":{"door":"doorS"},"D10":{"creature":"goblin"},"D12":{"creature":"goblin"},"F7":{"creature":"orc"},"G7":{"creature":"skeleton"},"H7":{"creature":"orc"},"C8":{"creature":"abomination"},"E3":{"creature":"mummy"},"M4":{"furniture":"chestN"},"O3":{"annotation":"letterG"},"P6":{"door":"doorW","annotation":"letterH"},"B3":{"furniture":"bookcaseN"},"B8":{"furniture":"throneN"},"H9":{"furniture":"tableW"},"G5":{"furniture":"fireplaceE"},"P8":{"furniture":"tombE"},"P7":{"creature":"dreadwarrior"},"R7":{"door":"doorS"},"S6":{"tile":"blockedwall"},"S14":{"door":"staircaseN"},"S12":{"annotation":"letterI"},"P2":{"creature":"goblin"},"Q2":{"creature":"goblin"},"P4":{"creature":"goblin"},"Q3":{"creature":"goblin"},"Q4":{"creature":"goblin"},"R4":{"creature":"goblin"},"R3":{"creature":"goblin"},"R2":{"creature":"goblin"}},"narrative":"Before%20they%20start%20their%20adventure%2C%20the%20girls%20want%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20their%20abilities.%20%20Let's%20see%20what%20they've%20got!%0A%0AIMPORTANT%20NOTE%3A%20This%20is%20a%20tutorial%20mission%20for%20those%20who%20feel%20they%20need%20it%2C%20and%20no%20items%20or%20GP%20found%20in%20this%20mission%20should%20carry%20over%20to%20the%20normal%20campaign.","notes":"%C2%A7MD%C2%A7**X**%20%3D%20The%20girls%20start%20here.%0A%0A*Welcome%20to%20Huntr%2Fx%20Quest.%20%20In%20this%20game%2C%20you%20will%20take%20the%20role%20of%20one%20of%20the%20famous%20Hunters%2C%20fighting%20demons%20and%20saving%20humanity.%0A%0AYou%20will%20be%20given%20an%20objective%20before%20every%20quest%2C%20and%20must%20move%2C%20engage%20in%20combat%2C%20solve%20problems%2C%20and%20carefully%20search%20your%20surroundings%20to%20achieve%20victory.%0A%0ATo%20begin%2C%20you%20find%20yourself%20in%20a%20corridor%20of%20the%20training%20halls.%20%20Find%20an%20entrance%20into%20the%20training%20rooms%20to%20begin.*%0A%0A**A**%20%3D%20*Before%20you%20appear%20two%20Goblins%3A%20the%20least%20dangerous%20of%20the%20demons%20you%20will%20encounter.%20%20Take%20them%20out%20with%20your%20Standard%20Attacks!%20%20You%20never%20run%20out%20of%20Standard%20Attacks%2C%20unlike%20your%20Abilities.*%0A%0AWhen%20this%20encounter%20is%20finished%20but%20before%20searching%2C%20say%3A%0A%0A*If%20you%20used%20any%20Rest%20abilities%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20Rest%20instead%20of%20searching%20for%20treasure.%20%20This%20choice%20is%20always%20available%20to%20you%20when%20you%20finish%20an%20encounter.%20%20Resting%20instead%20will%20recover%20all%20your%20used%20Rest%20abilities%2C%20but%20not%20your%20Quest%20ability%20if%20you%20used%20it.*%0A%0A**B**%20%3D%20*These%20are%20the%20slightly%20more%20dangerous%20Orcs%20and%20skeletons%3A%20also%20easily%20dispatched%2C%20but%20pack%20a%20bit%20more%20of%20a%20wallop.%20%20Skeletons%20can%20even%20attack%20diagonally!%20%20Mira%20and%20Zoey%2C%20if%20you%20have%20your%20Encounter%20ability%2C%20it%20might%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20use%20it%20to%20clear%20more%20than%20one%20enemy%20at%20the%20same%20time!*%0A%0A**C**%20%3D%20*In%20this%20room%20is%20a%20Fimir%2C%20an%20intimidating%20foe%20that%20can%20absorb%20multiple%20hits.%20%20It's%20tempting%20to%20use%20your%20Quest%20ability%20to%20take%20him%20out%20quickly%2C%20but%20remember%20you%20only%20get%20to%20use%20it%20once%20per%20quest!%20%20There's%20sure%20to%20be%20more%20fearsome%20enemies%20deeper%20in.%20%20Find%20another%20way%20to%20take%20him%20out.%20%20Rumi%2C%20your%20Encounter%20ability%20can%20make%20some%20of%20your%20dice%20rolls%20guaranteed%20hits%2C%20which%20might%20help%20here.%20%20Mira%2C%20you%20have%20a%20Taunt%20ability%20that%20can%20force%20the%20Fimir%20to%20attack%20you%20instead%20of%20one%20of%20your%20squishier%20friends.*%0A%0A**D**%20%3D%20*This%20room%20seems%20to%20be%20empty.%20%20Now%20might%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20use%20any%20healing%20abilities%20you%20have%20to%20recover%2C%20if%20you%20need%20it.*%0A%0A**E**%20%3D%20*This%20mummy%20gets%20the%20drop%20on%20you%20with%20a%20surprise%20attack!%20%20Zoey%2C%20now%20might%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20use%20your%20dodge%20or%20counterattack%20ability.%20%20They%20are%20unique%20in%20that%20they%20can%20be%20used%20on%20the%20enemy's%20turn.*%0A%0AWhen%20the%20mummy%20is%20defeated%20and%20the%20player%20searches%2C%20instead%20of%20pulling%20a%20treasure%20card%3A%0A%0A*Sometimes%20when%20you%20do%20a%20search%20after%20an%20encounter%2C%20you%20find%20a%20special%20event%20instead%20of%20pulling%20a%20random%20treasure.%20%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20mummy%20left%20behind%20a%20Potion%20of%20Concentrated%20Honmoon!%20%20This%20is%20very%20rare%20and%20valuable%3A%20only%20a%20couple%20exist%20in%20the%20world.%20%20Drinking%20this%20will%20restore%20all%20of%20your%20used%20Abilities%2C%20even%20the%20Quest%20and%20Rest%20abilties.*%0A%0A**F**%20%3D%20*Sometimes%20you'll%20find%20treasure%20chests.%20%20If%20you%20walk%20up%20to%20it%2C%20you%20can%20search%20it%20for%20special%20treasure.%20%20But%20beware!%20%20Sometimes%20they%20have%20traps.%20%20You%20can%20use%20your%20action%20to%20Search%20for%20a%20trap%20before%20you%20loot%20it.*%0A%0AThe%20chest%20has%20a%20dart%20trap%2C%20that%20deals%201%20BP%20of%20damage%20if%20not%20disabled.%20%20Inside%2C%20it%20contains%203%20Potions%20of%20Healing.%20%20*The%20potions%20of%20healing%20can%20recover%20your%20lost%20damage%2C%20and%20since%20you%20can%20use%20them%20at%20any%20time%20they%20can%20even%20save%20you%20from%20being%20knocked%20unconscious!*%0A%0A**G**%20%3D%20*There's%20lots%20of%20enemies%20here%2C%20but%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20stupified!%20%20A%20good%20opportunity%20to%20try%20Mira's%20crowd%20control%20attacks%2C%20or%20Zoey's%20ability%20to%20hit%20multiple%20targets.*%0A%0AThese%20enemies%20neither%20move%20nor%20attack.%20%20On%20Gwi-Ma's%20turn%2C%20say%20*The%20enemies%20look%20dazed%20and%20confused.*%0A%0A**H**%20%3D%20*A%20fearsome%20foe!%20%20Throw%20everything%20you've%20got%20at%20this%20Chaos%20Warrior!%20%20This%20is%20a%20good%20time%20to%20use%20your%20Quest%20abilities%3A%20you%20get%20the%20feeling%20this%20training%20session%20is%20almost%20over.%20%20Rumi%20is%20particularly%20well%20suited%20to%20fight%20single%2C%20strong%20monsters%20with%20her%20Quest%20ability%20that%20can%20dramatically%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20dice%20she%20rolls%20in%20combat.%20%20And%20remember%2C%20potions%20you%20found%20in%20this%20tutorial%20aren't%20kept%2C%20so%20use%20them%20all!*%0A%0A**I**%20%3D%20*You%20find%20the%20staircase%20out%20of%20the%20training%20grounds.%20%20Your%20test%20is%20complete%3A%20you're%20ready%20for%20anything.*","wanderingMonster":"Goblin","style":"hq-us"}]